notes: The American Community Survey does not cover employment among self-employed workers and employment in private households. Values do not include those employed in military occupations or attending primary or secondary school. Values includes those age 25 and older. Earnings are wage income over the previous 12 months. Wage values are rounded to the nearest 1,000.
